<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>USITC Questionnaire API</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>
        USITC Questionnaires API
    </h1>
    <p>
        This API provides functionality to extract questionnaire response data from Microsoft Word documents containing form fields or content controls.
    </p>
    <h2>
        INSTRUCTIONS
    </h2>
    <ul>
        <li>
            Files must be in '.docx' format.
        </li>
        <li>
            Files must contain either form fields or content controls.
        </li>
        <li>
            The response format (form fields, content controls) are handled by separate endpoints: "/FormFields" and "/ContentControls".
        </li>
        <li>
            The output format can be modified by appending "?format=[FORMAT]" to the URL, where '[FORMAT]' is 'xml', 'json', or 'csv'.
        </li>
    </ul>
    <form method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" asp-controller="Upload" asp-action="Post">
        <div class="form-group">
            <div class="col-md-10">
                <p>Upload one or more files using this form:</p>
                <input type="file" name="files" multiple />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <div class="col-md-10">
                <input type="submit" value="Upload" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </form>
</body>
</html>